- Improve stability and continuity of pinging process when interrupted/timeout occurs

- Implement the -i flag to change interval between packets

- Refactor code for better readability and maintainability

- Improve the packet size flag to match standard ping behavior

- Implement tracking of sequence:

// structure globale
bool g_ping.ping_recv_seq[65536]; // Pour toutes les séquences possibles (16 bits)

// dans ping_receive()
uint16_t recv_seq = ntohs(icmp->un.echo.sequence);

if (received_sequences[recv_seq]) {
    // vrai doublon
    g_ping.ping_num_rept++;
    if (g_ping.ping_flag_v) {
        printf("(DUP!)");
    }
} else {
    // premiere fois qu'on reçoit cette séquence
    received_sequences[recv_seq] = true;
    g_ping.ping_num_recv++;
}